.double-padded.border-regular-light-gray
  %h4 Accessibility
  %ul
    %li 
      Surround a related set of checkboxes with a 
      %code
        :escaped
          <fieldset>
      %span . 
      The
      %code
        :escaped
          <legend> 
      provides context for the grouping. Do not use fieldset and legend for a single check.
    %li 
      The custom checkboxes here are accessible to screen readers because the default checkboxes are moved off-screen with 
      %code
        position: absolute; left: -999em
      %span .
    %li 
      Each input should have a semantic 
      %code id 
      attribute, and its corresponding label should have the same value in it’s 
      %code 
        for 
      attribute.
    %li 
      The 
      %code title 
      attribute can replace
      %code
        :escaped
          <label>
      %span .

